description: NSLOCTEXT("", "71C9F0FC478B63B85BAED2959CF00CBC", "Oakenbane Keep was once a proud Kaelar tradition that reached back to the days of the founding of the Aelan Empire. What was once a foremost academy for promising recruits to learn from their venerable forebears is now a ruin filled with wandering shades. We have no explanation for these unquiet dead, but Ryland Hawkens, a military historian, assumes they suffer in this state. He\'s asked me to find the source of the haunting and put their spirits to rest.")
